{"tid":1606551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑新疆武警落黎香港執法！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-30T15:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T11:43:27.000Z","uid":293012,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb8ae684f942f8b7a7ca6a481e64387b53b6608","tid":1606551,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"（代人post）<br />\n<br />\nGlock 26係中國鎮壓新疆人部隊吧武器。香港機場特警裝備Glock 17。但從槍柄長度黎睇似Glock 26多啲。<br />\n嗰個臥底採用茶杯式握槍姿勢，個姿勢係錯嘅，非常容易因為後坐力而受傷，香港警隊採用英國SAS訓練課程係使用韋佛式握槍。<br />\n就算面對嘅係民眾示威，SAS訓練指引應當降低重心，而嗰個掹槍臥底反而駝背挺肚。很明顯唔係SAS系統受訓。<br />\n而嗰個臥底嘅肌肉以及面對示威者嘅反應好顯然係槍枝使用嘅老手。<br />\n<br />\n結合前日嘅軍車大巴，北京很大機會已派左新疆進行鎮壓的武裝部隊入港並且上街執法。由於新疆鎮壓部隊習慣於使用不對等武力以及毫無人性的殘殺，佢地對示威者嘅態度極其輕蔑殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n感謝支那維基嘅管理員李威提供槍枝以及軍事訓練方面嘅分析。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnqPF4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnqPF4P.png&h=770ec21b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e4a73044d3fe7dbd0360854f58f96f14d59aa","tid":1606551,"uid":91205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec4446c6bf39668f22f5b607f6e44d722523a65","tid":1606551,"uid":53666,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"即係唔係差佬啦<br />\n市民係咪可以用高一級武力去制止<br />\n<br />\n以後再見, 一定要佢跌裝"},{"pid":"adc89c898750018f7d873ce3c0244b677cf6f6cd","tid":1606551,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"Telegram預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"a54b0b3266398882932d243e14b41b18bd6eebe0","tid":1606551,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20